Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等水在沙槽裡積起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜歡水傾瀉而出的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看著水決堤 得以解放 奔流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沙槽裡蓄滿的能量爆發開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都會動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玉木真理小姐 都已經中午囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我好像做了個噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽舉著條濕毛巾往我臉上蓋 想謀殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那還真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我昨天有叫你收拾房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上高中想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寫日記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曠一次課
