Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我打算先去東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後來場說走就走的旅行 隨心漂泊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Enjoy your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我要逃學了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是要請假逃學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得這點想法挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道小理 你沒逃過學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠 你逃過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有人沒逃過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別用那種眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你試過說走就走的旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那倒是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼知道我要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你會想些什麼 我還不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種旅行 一個人才有意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就放心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好興奮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天就在車站的廁所換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是大海耶 大海！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了 會被發現是群馬縣人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.88,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※群馬縣是日本少有的內陸縣。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}姊姊你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼早就要出門啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那包包是要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟朋友借了運動服還沒還
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又借了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用擔心 我打過電話給老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}學你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你得在外住一晚 我會跟你統一說詞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用擔心 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在廁所換上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搭上與學校反方向的火車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個人逃離平時的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}踏上說走就走的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去一個陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外面下雨了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且我覺得 逃學是不好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒有想去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有啊 有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}京都 沖繩 北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你怎麼沒去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛機說不定會墜毀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新幹線說不定會爆炸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隕石說不定會從天而降？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你怎麼沒走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我總是會這樣
