Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想加社團的時候 想學東西的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想挑戰名校的入學考試的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全都在事到臨頭前退怯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦嘗試沒有做過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總會想不順利的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想要失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會不會後悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每到最後關頭總會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得這也不是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:17.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\1c&H242D2B&\t(0,5780,0\fs40)\frz346.2\move(596,274,596,270,0,5754)}門禁前會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:17.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\1c&H353939&\t(0,5780,0\fs40)\frz344.3\move(70,388,44,384,0,5754)}我做了常吃的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最討厭自己這一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次要不要一起出去玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 你東西掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 總共多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}數了一下 正好100萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你拿來幹嘛 要送去警局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家嚇到忘記了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真會找藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啦 我認真的 真的是嚇呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且掉了這個信封的人 好像是穿我們學校的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幾年級的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是瞄到她的背影一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}髮型和那邊那位很像 大概是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味道很香 潤絲的香味？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這點線索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 頭髮那麼長的人大概不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去看看一年級的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靜不下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬元…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 其實昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 我沒騙你 真的是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寫這本書的人是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前是南極觀測員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我上國中的時候 她突然下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後沒找到人 基本上也沒什麼遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想去找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極嗎？你能去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家也是這種反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外婆 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師 學長 還有鄰居
